HEADWORD: Parabolism
<hw>Pa*rab"o*lism</hw> <pr>(p⟦adot⟧*r⟦acr⟧b"⟦osl⟧*l⟦icr⟧z'm)</pr>,
<pos>n.</pos> <ety>[From <er>Parabola</er>.]</ety> <fld>(Alg.)</fld>
<def>The division of the terms of an equation by a known quantity that
is involved in the first term.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

